title: THE FINALE | YouTube Censors COVID Doctors | Ep 14 Good Morning MugClub
description: What do you think of YouTube’s censoring anything that disagrees with the WHO? Do you think banning the discussion of potential COVID-19 treatments could actually prevent possible COVID-19 treatments from being researched further? Also, more insane rambling from AOC about how COVID-19 and climate change are interconnected, Chloroquine Lady faces criminal charges for feeding her husband fish tank cleaner, and we end with a roast of Jocko Willink, performed by our Jocko correspondent.
